SliTaz Mirror
===============================================================================


Files and tools used on mirror1.slitaz.org including web interface info. Images
and CSS style are hosted on MF and aliases are widely used for replication.

	* files : Custom system configuration files
	* info  : Mirror web interface at http://mirror1.slitaz.org/info/
	* root  : File for the root directory of http://mirror1.slitaz.org/

Host : mirror1.slitaz.org
IP   : 188.165.229.172


Administration
--------------
To update a virtual host files manually you can use the mirror utility.
If you want to update the static files on mirror and Tiny SliTaz:

# mirror up-mirror
# mirror up-tiny


